#!new # vim:syntax=markdown:tw=0

# BRIEF
#! Create an Apache 2.0 license

=pod

=head1 NAME

B<apache2.0 OWNER> - Create an Apache 2.0 license

=head1 SYNOPSIS

B<new> apache2.0 'OWNER NAME'

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Simply creates a LICENSE file referencing the OWNER and Apache 2.0 license.

